  "instructions": [
    "Heat olive oil in a large pot over medium heat.",
    "Add diced onion and cook until translucent, about 5 minutes.",
    "Stir in minced garlic, diced carrot, and diced sweet potato; cook for 5 more minutes.",
    "Add split peas, tomato paste, cumin, coriander, and smoked paprika; stir until peas are coated and fragrant.",
    "Pour in vegetable broth and bring to a boil.",
    "Reduce heat to low, cover, and simmer for 35 minutes until the peas are tender and the sauce has thickened.",
    "Season with salt and black pepper, tasting and adjusting as needed.",
    "Serve hot, garnished with chopped fresh cilantro."
